---
title: Thai-Spiced Pork & Ginger-Coconut Rice with Crispy Shallots Top rated | Available all April
description: It's a good thing this Thai dish is quick and easy to make because it smells so amazing as it cooks that it's tempting to eat it straight from
the pan! But it's worth the wait, especially for the ginger-coconut rice which has got to be the tastiest accompaniment around.
